19 Hours Ago Meanwhile, the Nigerian Army has scheduled today for the second edition of a spiritual warfare seminar to counter Boko Haram propaganda. Acting Director, Army Public Relations, Col. Sagir Musa, disclosed this yesterday in an invitation sent to journalists. The army had, last year October in Sokoto launched the first edition of a joint seminar on spiritual warfare against insurgency and other forms of restiveness.